    <section id="privacy">
      <h3>Privacy policies</h3>

      <h2>1. Overview</h2>
      <p>This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the Aruna Grands Hotel Booking System.</p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>a) Personal Information:</strong> Full name, Contact number, Email address, ID proof, Address details</p>
      <p><strong>b) Booking & Payment Details:</strong> Check-in/out dates, Room preferences, Payment method, Transaction ID and booking history</p>
      <p><strong>c) Device & Usage Data:</strong> IP address, Browser/device info, Pages visited, time spent, Click-stream data</p>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your data to: Process bookings and payments, Contact you for confirmations, updates, or offers, Improve website performance and personalization, Prevent fraud or abuse, Comply with legal obligations</p>

      <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your data. We only share information with: Payment gateway partners (for secure transactions), Government/law enforcement (only if legally required), Customer support or IT service vendors under confidentiality</p>

      <h2>5. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to remember preferences and improve speed. You can disable cookies in your browser but some features may not work properly.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
      <p>All data is encrypted via HTTPS and stored securely. Passwords are hashed using industry-standard techniques. Admins and staff are trained on data protection best practices.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Right to access your data, Right to correct inaccuracies, Right to request deletion, Right to opt-out of marketing emails (unsubscribe anytime)</p>

      <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain data only as long as necessary: Booking history: up to 1 year, Account info: until you request deletion</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to Policy</h2>
      <p>This policy may be updated from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@arunagrands.com">privacy@arunagrands.com</a></p>
